  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\n`@truffle/events` uses `ora` but does not declare this dependency in `package.json`\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate a project that requires `@truffle/events`. (In my case, I was depending on `@truffle/config`, which in turn depends on`@truffle/events` ). Try to run it.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThings should run normally.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nRunning the project fails with the error:\r\n\r\n```\r\nError: Cannot find module 'ora'\r\n    at Function.Module._resolveFilename (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:636:15)\r\n    at Function.Module._load (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:562:25)\r\n    at Module.require (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:692:17)\r\n    at require (internal/modules/cjs/helpers.js:25:18)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/var/app/current/node_modules/@truffle/events/defaultSubscribers/obtain.js:1:13)\r\n    at Module._compile (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:778:30)\r\n    at Object.Module._extensions..js (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:789:10)\r\n    at Module.load (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:653:32)\r\n    at tryModuleLoad (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:593:12)\r\n    at Function.Module._load (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:585:3)\r\n    at Module.require (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:692:17)\r\n    at require (internal/modules/cjs/helpers.js:25:18)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/var/app/current/node_modules/@truffle/events/defaultSubscribers/index.js:3:11)\r\n    at Module._compile (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:778:30)\r\n    at Object.Module._extensions..js (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:789:10)\r\n    at Module.load (internal/modules/cjs/loader.js:653:32)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: various\r\n* Ethereum client: various\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): Truffle v5.1.18 (core: 5.1.18)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): Node v10.16.3\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.9.0\r\n",
